summary:
So, this morning my cat, Ermal, jumped on my bookshelf and threw down my beloved Funko Kylo. He didn't make it :(
But the worst...
body:
RIP FUNKO KYLO

So, this morning my cat, Ermal, jumped on my bookshelf and threw down my beloved Funko Kylo. He didn’t make it :(

But the worst part was my brother, that after he saw that mess laughed and said: “Oh, look! A spoiler from Episode IX!!”

Right now, I don’t know if I should kill my cat or my brother…
